reviewtext: The sound is just fair - Cheap Sony headphones sound much better.  And despite purchasing these through Amazon Prime, the seller was going to let me return them after I paid shipping and reshelfing fees, which together added up to more than the headphones.  I had purchased two sets and this return applied to only the unopened set.  Now I have two worthless headphones.
